title: WHAT'S Going on in Antarctica?! | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 31
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


HAPPY 4TH OF JULY BABES!!! THE BABES talk Chris' new obsession ANTARCTICA. What team has the best mascot ever? How do Penguins identify? Can you eat Panda meat? Sal loves Hello Kitty. What's really going on in Antarctica! Was the lost city of Atlantis once in Antarctica?! Chris breaks down all the mysteries of Antarctica. Were the Nazi's there doing stuff to aliens?! UFO's and a hidden Civilization. Should the babes go to Antarctica. SOUND OFF IN THE COMMENTS. Sal has every phone number he's gotten since the 90s on his phone....how many people can a human know? THIS IS THE ADHD PODCAST YAS! The babes tallk about the guy in Cape Cod who got swallowed by a whale. We ask Sal as a germaphobe what he would do inside of the whale. Chris has run into some issues with poison control. July 4th Facts! Sal has a freaky incident with the Police. Nathan's Hot Dog Eating Contest is fun. What is the difference between goats vs sheep vs lamb vs rams?! WHAT!


Rate us on iTunes!
